dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Washburn_Roads_2015.gdb.[This data set consists of digital map files containing road centerline information obtained primarily by conducting lab work using aerial imagery and other data sources. Features contained in the data set include all public and private named roads countywide and associated attributes. The Washburn County plans to maintain this digital data in ESRI's ArcGIS 9.x geodatabase environment using ArcMap tools. Some of the data was developed using field data collection techniques and field data collection will be used extensively to maintain the data. There are attributes in the data documenting the source for each record.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://co.washburn.wi.us/gis-data-downloads/
